{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bb46378827","title":"中央农运讲习所招生计划","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"92b873641f","index":0,"year":1927,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"bb46378827"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"13664c6072","type":"paragraph","text":"中央农运讲习所招生计划","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"42e1684e9d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1927年6月）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"5ec79c388a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、学额一共六百名，第二期学额分配，应注重北方各省尤应多招直鲁豫三省学生，湘鄂赣农运人员已有相当准备，暂不招生，其他各省，则了量支配。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"a281bdd4ee","type":"paragraph","text":"学额省别","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"cfcc1937f5","type":"paragraph","text":"八十鲁直","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"a15909cc13","type":"paragraph","text":"八十","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"a85caacd83","type":"paragraph","text":"八十豫","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"55b74d3a27","type":"paragraph","text":"五十陕","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"b65d9617c3","type":"paragraph","text":"五十晋","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"57c6fe867e","type":"paragraph","text":"五十川","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"1d0750d5f1","type":"paragraph","text":"三十皖","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"b0780649ea","type":"paragraph","text":"五十苏","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"ff337a78a8","type":"paragraph","text":"三十奉热","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"8e795520e2","type":"paragraph","text":"十五","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"5716cfb006","type":"paragraph","text":"十察","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"ccd99cd53e","type":"paragraph","text":"绥","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"5655da5d88","type":"paragraph","text":"二十闽","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"595cd2f047","type":"paragraph","text":"二十浙","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"a860a05cb2","type":"paragraph","text":"二十五其他","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"9aea84c381","type":"paragraph","text":"二、开学日期定于九月一日。因第一届须六月底始能结束，结束后，须稍有休歇时间，整理一切，且北方各省招生，亦须相当时间，故须九月一日，始能开学","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"6875a45bfe","type":"paragraph","text":"三、招生办法学生仍由各省党部依据第一期招生章程，负责考送。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"157dff3929","type":"paragraph","text":"四、课程训练根据第一届所定办法办理五、学习期间仍定为四月，即今年十二月底毕业","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"d755979880","type":"paragraph","text":"六、班数仍为四班，依第一届之经验，每班学生人数过多，管理训练，极形不便。故二届学生，应的量减少，第一届每班二百人以上至二百五十人，第二届应减至一百五十人，故六百人仍为四班。","index":22,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"991cc5199a","type":"paragraph","text":"七、经费第二届经费支出及收入，均与第一届有不相同处即第一届经费有四万元，系湘鄂赣三省党部负担，第二届经费，须完全由中央负担，因北方各省，尚无能力分任也，又第一届学生来所，并无路费，支出回籍路费，口比较不多，第二届学生则来所回籍，均须发给路费，故路费支出，为数甚巨，来往路费共三万元，预算如下表","index":23,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"7727334d9e","type":"paragraph","text":"省别","index":24,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"348fb228e7","type":"paragraph","text":"每名数（元）","index":25,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"eb18a8474d","type":"paragraph","text":"共计（元）鲁","index":26,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"e0b5c92c42","type":"paragraph","text":"五十","index":27,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"a10d16a59c","type":"paragraph","text":"四干直","index":28,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"041fc88592","type":"paragraph","text":"五十","index":29,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"42bf2faf79","type":"paragraph","text":"四干豫","index":30,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"40199024d1","type":"paragraph","text":"三十","index":31,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"ce3f77e00b","type":"paragraph","text":"二千四百陕","index":32,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"5258706b91","type":"paragraph","text":"七十","index":33,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"3e5a205a2b","type":"paragraph","text":"三千五百晋","index":34,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"965eb449fb","type":"paragraph","text":"六十","index":35,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"027b02f6f9","type":"paragraph","text":"三千川","index":36,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"8711af9a3e","type":"paragraph","text":"四千","index":37,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"08d6240771","type":"paragraph","text":"八十皖","index":38,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"9870af4658","type":"paragraph","text":"二十","index":39,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"d9a2338fdb","type":"paragraph","text":"六百","index":40,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"d6f634e33b","type":"paragraph","text":"共计（元）","index":41,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"95404a7214","type":"paragraph","text":"每名数（元）省别","index":42,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"4873ac2c79","type":"paragraph","text":"一千二百","index":43,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"7afd3aa9c8","type":"paragraph","text":"十四苏","index":44,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"da35a0b6d7","type":"paragraph","text":"二千四百","index":45,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"7fa0e01fe6","type":"paragraph","text":"八十本","index":46,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"060d513ff7","type":"paragraph","text":"一千零五十","index":47,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"ab530600b7","type":"paragraph","text":"七十热","index":48,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"5824548c42","type":"paragraph","text":"四十","index":49,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"ccf285467d","type":"paragraph","text":"八百闽","index":50,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"af4bd60a26","type":"paragraph","text":"六百","index":51,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"7df31a4c9c","type":"paragraph","text":"三十浙","index":52,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"ae152f1bfc","type":"paragraph","text":"七百","index":53,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"984aa214d9","type":"paragraph","text":"七十察","index":54,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"2705d27ee1","type":"paragraph","text":"七十","index":55,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"da46719877","type":"paragraph","text":"七百绥","index":56,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"6d12a88ac7","type":"paragraph","text":"一百零五","index":57,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"045af69b56","type":"paragraph","text":"其他经常费共六方六千元","index":58,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"f24f77c493","type":"paragraph","text":"（说明）依第一届经验每学生一人四个月需用费一百一十元，六百人六万六千元。","index":59,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"},{"id":"5a774325ff","type":"paragraph","text":"以上两项，共需九万六千元，拟由七月份起，仍按第一届，向中央支领一万四千元之数，则中央每月支出之预算，仍然不变。","index":60,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827"}],"page":{"id":"784af9cce7","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"bb46378827","start":34,"end":36}}}},"__N_SSG":true}